data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of LaBelle, Florida! This stunning single-family residence boasts 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and a convenient 3-car garage, providing ample space for your family and vehicles. *** Property is tenant occupied with a month to month rent at $1,500.00 per month.  Tenant will move out 30 days from effective date of the contract.  ***This new construction home was completed in 2021, offering the perfect blend of contemporary design and comfort. The interior features an open-concept layout, allowing natural light to flood the living spaces, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout.   Safety and security are paramount, and this property is thoughtfully equipped with hurricane impact windows, providing peace of mind during storm seasons. You can rest easy knowing your family and belongings are well-protected.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your forever home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the true essence of Florida living at its finest!
